		<title>郭智輝官場適應力提升 綠委：改革企圖心不容忽視</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/02/%e9%83%ad%e6%99%ba%e8%bc%9d%e5%ae%98%e5%a0%b4%e9%81%a9%e6%87%89%e5%8a%9b%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87-%e7%b6%a0%e5%a7%94%ef%bc%9a%e6%94%b9%e9%9d%a9%e4%bc%81%e5%9c%96%e5%bf%83%e4%b8%8d%e5%ae%b9%e5%bf%bd%e8%a6%96/</link>
		
