					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="2048" height="2048" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/image-91.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/image-91.png?w=2048&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/image-91.png?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/image-91.png?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/image-91.png?resize=1536%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/image-91.png?resize=146%2C146&amp;ssl=1 146w" sizes="(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px" /></p>
<p>由平民時報工作人員撰寫 / 2025年3月31日 一種新的加密貨幣讓中國共產黨感到恐慌。他們不再壟斷公民的交易 &#8230;</p>
